In the EU, PIMFA is a member of the following formal networks: Financial Future; BIPAR and the European Retail Financial Forum (ERFF).  PIMFA also participates informally in a full range of Brussels-based networking events.&#xd;
&#xd;
In the UK, PIMFA is a member of the following formal groups, as well as participating in a range of informal networking events: Joint Money Laundering Steering Group (JMLSG); Joint Trade Association Group (JTAG); Trade Association Co-ordinating Committee (TACC); The International Regulatory Strategy Group (IRSG); and The City UK.
